<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/691483-in-the-last-few-pages-there-is-a-british">In the last few pages there is a British stranger (seems to be white, non-Indian) who vists Parvati in Mayapore, where she now lives with Lili Chatterjee. Who is the stranger? Is it Colin Lindsey? Or are we not supposed to know? If it&#39;s revealed in later novels, don&#39;t say who it is.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_691483'><a id="like_count_community_question_691483" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/691483?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F146746.The_Jewel_in_the_Crown">like</a></span>

